# 아파트 실거래 매매 API 불러오기



```python
import ssl
from urllib.request import urlopen
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import pandas as pd

ServiceKey = '???'
month = 202412
gu_code = 11650
numOfRows = 1000


url = 'https://apis.data.go.kr/1613000/RTMSDataSvcAptTrade/getRTMSDataSvcAptTrade?serviceKey='+str(ServiceKey)+'&LAWD_CD='+str(gu_code)+'&DEAL_YMD='+str(month)+'&numOfRows='+str(numOfRows)

context = ssl.create_default_context()
context.set_ciphers('DEFAULT:@SECLEVEL=1') 

result = urlopen(url, context = context)
house = BeautifulSoup(result, 'lxml-xml')
te = house.find_all('item')


data =[]

for i in range(len(te)):
    price = te[i].dealAmount.string.strip()
    built_yr = te[i].buildYear.string.strip()
    dong_name = te[i].umdNm.string.strip()
    apt_name = te[i].aptNm.string.strip()
    size = te[i].excluUseAr.string.strip()
    gu_code = te[i].sggCd.string.strip()
    
    total = [month,price,built_yr,dong_name,apt_name,size,gu_code]
    data.append(total)

temp = pd.DataFrame(data, columns=['month','price','built_yr','dong_name','apt_name','size','gu_code'])
temp.to_csv('house_price.csv')
```


```python
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

df = pd.read_csv('house_price.csv')
df = df.drop('Unnamed: 0', axis=1)

df['size_pyung'] = df['size']/3.33
df['price'] = df['price'].replace({'[^0-9.]':''}, regex=True).astype('float')
df['price_pyung'] = df['price']/df['size_pyung']
df.describe()

df.to_csv('house_price.csv')
```

# 국토교통부 아파트 전월세 



```python
import ssl
from urllib.request import urlopen
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import pandas as pd

ServiceKey = '???'
month = 202412
gu_code = 11650
numOfRows = 1000


url = 'https://apis.data.go.kr/1613000/RTMSDataSvcAptRent/getRTMSDataSvcAptRent?serviceKey='+str(ServiceKey)+'&LAWD_CD='+str(gu_code)+'&DEAL_YMD='+str(month)+'&numOfRows='+str(numOfRows)

context = ssl.create_default_context()
context.set_ciphers('DEFAULT:@SECLEVEL=1') 

result = urlopen(url, context = context)
house = BeautifulSoup(result, 'lxml-xml')
te = house.find_all('item')


data =[]

for i in range(len(te)):
    secu_de = te[i].deposit.string.strip()
    month_rent = te[i].monthlyRent.string.strip()
    built_yr = te[i].buildYear.string.strip()
    dong_name = te[i].umdNm.string.strip()
    apt_name = te[i].aptNm.string.strip()
    size = te[i].excluUseAr.string.strip()
    gu_code = te[i].sggCd.string.strip()
    
    total_apt_month_rent = [month,secu_de,month_rent,built_yr,dong_name,apt_name,size,gu_code]
    data.append(total_apt_month_rent)

apt_monthRent = pd.DataFrame(data, columns=['month','secu_de','month_rent','built_yr','dong_name','apt_name','size','gu_code'])
apt_monthRent.to_csv('apt_monthRent_price.csv')
apt_monthRent
```

```python
import ssl
from urllib.request import urlopen
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import pandas as pd

ServiceKey = '???'
baseDate = 20250310
numOfRows = 3000


url = 'https://apis.data.go.kr/1160100/service/GetKrxListedInfoService/getItemInfo?serviceKey='+str(ServiceKey)+'&basDt='+str(baseDate)+'&numOfRows='+str(numOfRows)

context = ssl.create_default_context()
context.set_ciphers('DEFAULT:@SECLEVEL=1') 

result = urlopen(url, context = context)
house = BeautifulSoup(result, 'lxml-xml')
te = house.find_all('item')


data =[]

for i in range(len(te)):
    date = te[i].basDt.string.strip()
    market = te[i].mrktCtg.string.strip()
    name = te[i].itmsNm.string.strip()
    fullName = te[i].corpNm.string.strip()
    code = te[i].srtnCd.string.strip()
    fullCode = te[i].isinCd.string.strip()
    bubinCode = te[i].crno.string.strip()
    
    total = [date, market, name, fullName, code, fullCode, bubinCode]
    data.append(total)

krx = pd.DataFrame(data, columns=['date', 'market', 'name', 'fullName', 'code', 'fullCode', 'bubinCode'])
krx.to_csv('krx.csv')
```

```python
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
from urllib.request import urlopen
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup
import ssl

ServiceKey = '???'
stockCode = '066570'
numOfRows = 10000
beginDay = 20240101
endDay = 20250301

url = 'https://apis.data.go.kr/1160100/service/GetStockSecuritiesInfoService/getStockPriceInfo?serviceKey='+str(ServiceKey)+'&numOfRows='+str(numOfRows)+'&beginBasDt='+str(beginDay)+'&endBasDt='+str(endDay)+'&likeSrtnCd='+str(stockCode)

context = ssl.create_default_context()
context.set_ciphers('DEFAULT:@SECLEVEL=1') 

results = urlopen(url, context = context)
stock = BeautifulSoup(results, 'lxml-xml')
te = stock.find_all('item')

data = []
for i in range(len(te)):
    date =  te[i].basDt.string.strip()
    market = te[i].mrktCtg.string.strip()
    close = te[i].clpr.string.strip()
    start = te[i].mkp.string.strip()
    high = te[i].hipr.string.strip()
    low = te[i].lopr.string.strip()
    stockCode = te[i].srtnCd.string.strip()
    stockName = te[i].itmsNm.string.strip()
    volume = te[i].trqu.string.strip()
    amount = te[i].trPrc.string.strip()
    totShare = te[i].lstgStCnt.string.strip()
    totAmount = te[i].mrktTotAmt.string.strip()
    total = [date, stockCode, stockName, market, close, start, high, low, volume, amount, totShare, totAmount]
    data.append(total)

temp = pd.DataFrame(data, columns = ['date', 'stockCode', 'stockName', 'market', 'close', 'start', 'high', 'low', 'volume', 'amount', 'totShare', 'totAmount'])
temp.to_csv('lg_price.csv',index=False )    
```
